# {{lb|zh|Cantonese}} [[skinny]]; [[lean]]
# {{lb|zh|Cantonese}} to [[hurt]] (the [[stomach]])
# {{lb|zh|Hokkien}} to [[mock]]; to [[ridicule]]; to have a [[dig]] at someone {{gl|to embarrass someone}}
# {{lb|zh|Xiamen Hokkien}} to [[remove]] [[fat]], etc. from a [[body]] [[organ]] {{gl|of food or beverage}}
